{"id": "1321571433738014741", "channel_id": "1321571433738014741", "type": 0, "author_id": "856264437078163496", "author_name": "tianjiu5993", "author_bot": false, "content": "最近玩了绝区零 感觉他们的养成引导做的很好 可以很明切的知道要刷什么材料和仪器 和比较常见的配队  而且还可以知道哪些是大多数人会用的仪器 \n\n所以我想问下忘却也能不能搞这种类似的东西出来，感觉会很方便萌新\n举个例子我现在想要刷血希的密契 我要先去b站 youtube 上搜索各种视频 有些视频还是很久以前的了 经过很久的搜索才成功的找到血希要的是什么密契", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T20:13:03.413000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-12-25T20:13:19.052000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "ld_CheemsRheart", "emoji_id": "864769327265873920", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1321571499538386960", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-12-26-04-11-55-199_com.HoYoverse.Nap.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 132221, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1321571433738014741/1321571499538386960/Screenshot_2024-12-26-04-11-55-199_com.HoYoverse.Nap.jpg?ex=69cc2adf&is=69cad95f&hm=ff677f2aa1b7a1c9cb2c296d2beb12a87a65ece1c49a7155b545f5155bcaf4fe&"}, {"id": "1321571500356141066", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-12-26-04-11-42-745_com.HoYoverse.Nap.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 123241, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1321571433738014741/1321571500356141066/Screenshot_2024-12-26-04-11-42-745_com.HoYoverse.Nap.jpg?ex=69cc2adf&is=69cad95f&hm=839c174b00e072da394983e8f8c1e0ed188bf7d6c32263ac396284daac34bfcc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321571433738014741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于养成机制的一些小建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
