{"id": "1321616420320051262", "channel_id": "1321571433738014741", "type": 0, "author_id": "484622919943716864", "author_name": "sense25.", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果你有好好玩的话，打开幕间演习-幻梦深潜-调查排行，很容易找到别人的配队和装备，养成材料你在唤醒体界面消耗材料那可以也很容易找到需要的材料在哪产出", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T23:11:49.050000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321571433738014741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于养成机制的一些小建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1321617545543028877", "channel_id": "1321571433738014741", "type": 0, "author_id": "484622919943716864", "author_name": "sense25.", "author_bot": false, "content": "你说的这种当面喂饭的引导，感觉不会对太多人产生帮助，因为这是一个比较硬核的手游，和zzz的受众差别挺大，如果你连养成材料都找的很麻烦，很难想象你怎么打这游戏的主线", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T23:16:17.324000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321571433738014741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于养成机制的一些小建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1321384050920914986", "channel_id": "1321384050920914986", "type": 0, "author_id": "1313549043951206413", "author_name": "wuyaxiezitai", "author_bot": false, "content": "中午从端内客服那边问到了台服和港澳服的中奖问卷是不一样的，但是没来得及问其他的事校工就结束对话了，按现在这个说法台服的地址收集是比港澳服晚的，所以来dc问一下到时候也是台服的礼盒发货时间晚于港澳服吗<:wish:1236951537788649492> \n（附一下端内客服聊天截图）", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T07:48:27.868000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1321384051155931136", "filename": "Screenshot_20241225_144422_com_sialiagames_z1_gp_twnew_EjoyWebViewActivity.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 133377, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1321384050920914986/1321384051155931136/Screenshot_20241225_144422_com_sialiagames_z1_gp_twnew_EjoyWebViewActivity.jpg?ex=69cc250b&is=69cad38b&hm=6a1d32f348a5fb3b24809fc7b15d8c9265f08d509409cbe4820f7c950df1469d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321384050920914986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "来问一下关于周年礼盒的发货问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1321389071423242291", "channel_id": "1321384050920914986", "type": 0, "author_id": "1287351071693606924", "author_name": "tururu_37124", "author_bot": false, "content": "原来是这样，然而我是库卡账号也是只有邮箱🥲 ，我觉得发货应该是周边做好后统一发的吧。总共估计也是几百份不至于需要分批生产", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T08:08:24.849000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321384050920914986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "来问一下关于周年礼盒的发货问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1321389353985118218", "channel_id": "1321384050920914986", "type": 0, "author_id": "1123604182407073833", "author_name": "yummy_9673", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是台服的\n資料只能填電話號碼跟mail🤔🤔", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T08:09:32.217000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321384050920914986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "来问一下关于周年礼盒的发货问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1321391160220192778", "channel_id": "1321384050920914986", "type": 19, "author_id": "1313549043951206413", "author_name": "wuyaxiezitai", "author_bot": false, "content": "感觉可能台服这边是统一先收集邮件和电话，我是早上和群友聊才知道原来有些人问卷里就直接填地址了，以防万一问了客服，结果发货还没问就结束对话了，想着总归是要问清楚就来dc发贴了<:flop:1243504846062223360> 按理来说应该是统一发，但它问卷是分开的搞得我也不是很懂，问清楚点心里也踏实<:sigh:1236949926357766218>", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T08:16:42.857000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1287351071693606924"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1321389071423242291", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321384050920914986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "来问一下关于周年礼盒的发货问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1321391577674944553", "channel_id": "1321384050920914986", "type": 19, "author_id": "1313549043951206413", "author_name": "wuyaxiezitai", "author_bot": false, "content": "我也是台服了，估摸着台服和港澳服的问卷不一样，台服的问卷只有电话和邮件地址两个填空，群友说港澳的好像还有两个关于地址的填空<:stoppage:1236938521365839872>", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T08:18:22.386000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1123604182407073833"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1321389353985118218", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321384050920914986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "来问一下关于周年礼盒的发货问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1321392333752635432", "channel_id": "1321384050920914986", "type": 19, "author_id": "1287351071693606924", "author_name": "tururu_37124", "author_bot": false, "content": "卡墨是带地址的，昨天下午看他发的吓了我一跳，还以为我这里出bug了……不过我是港服啊为什么给我的是台服的问卷<:flop:1236937860922343466> ，希望能顺利领到吧<:flop:1236937860922343466>", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T08:21:22.649000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1313549043951206413"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1321391577674944553", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321384050920914986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "来问一下关于周年礼盒的发货问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1321393191601045514", "channel_id": "1321384050920914986", "type": 19, "author_id": "1313549043951206413", "author_name": "wuyaxiezitai", "author_bot": false, "content": "港服为什么会收到台服的问卷<:stoppage:1236938521365839872> ，不会真出bug了吧，要不你问问端内客服，虽然填了问卷按理来说应该能收到，希望大家都能顺利领到吧<:flop:1243504846062223360>", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T08:24:47.176000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1287351071693606924"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1321392333752635432", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321384050920914986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "来问一下关于周年礼盒的发货问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1321394614934175805", "channel_id": "1321384050920914986", "type": 19, "author_id": "1287351071693606924", "author_name": "tururu_37124", "author_bot": false, "content": "原来有端内客服的吗？我之前@露比她还没回我，感谢感谢，我去端内客服那边问问<:stoppage:1236938521365839872>", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T08:30:26.525000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1313549043951206413"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1321393191601045514", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321384050920914986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "来问一下关于周年礼盒的发货问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1321399333634969674", "channel_id": "1321384050920914986", "type": 19, "author_id": "1313549043951206413", "author_name": "wuyaxiezitai", "author_bot": false, "content": "有端内客服的，可以通过登录界面右边那一列里面有客服字样的图标或游戏内设置→账号→客服联系到，虽然回复也慢慢的，不过以防万一两边都问一下比较好<:think:1243504961254326354>", "timestamp": "2024-12-25T08:49:11.551000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1287351071693606924"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1321394614934175805", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321384050920914986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "来问一下关于周年礼盒的发货问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
